<div class="staff-title pad">
<div id="imageContent544e3c4ef857406f91bc7f30696a72f1">
</div>
<h3 id="member50">Louise Soanes</h3>
<p><em>TCT Nurse Consultant for Adolescents and Yong Adults</em></p>
<p>Louise has worked at The Royal Marsden since 2002, and has been nurse consultant for adolescents and young adults since 2008. She works with teams across the trust and partner hospitals to establish AYA care cancer.</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:lsoanes@nhs.net">lsoanes@nhs.net</a></p>
</div>
<div class="staff-info pad">
<h4>Qualifications</h4>
<p>RSCN/RGN</p>
